As I was dancing @ecstaticdancela on the beach with a bunch of like-minded individuals two police officers pulled up in a police buggy to watch. I immediately wondered if there was a threat to our safety.  I imagined  being joyful at a dance festival and all of a sudden everyone around you is being shot to death. I’ve never felt so grateful for my freedom and safety. Please goddess help this world 🌎 🫶

Today I was a butterfly. I wasn’t Jewish. I was just a butterfly. I didn’t have the memory lingering in the back of my mind of my family house being marked and numbered because I was Jewish.  I didn’t have the memory of my family, friends and community being sent to gas chambers. Today I was only a butterfly 🦋
